## Description
The Telomere project aims to establish a robust, reproducible workflow for estimating telomere length from whole-genome sequencing (WGS) data. It integrates with the LC/MCAOA platform to enable large-scale cohort analysis, quality control, and downstream statistical modeling. The project will deliver a validated pipeline, reference datasets, and documentation for use by the research community.

